data.description: Fantastic home in a prime location! This property offers easy access to everything Plano has to offer, including world-class shopping, dining, and entertainment options. Additionally, Plano's excellent schools. This home has bright and open interior with plenty of natural light and a neutral color palate, complimented by a fireplace. The kitchen is ready for cooking with ample counter space, REFRIGERATOR INCLUDED! Relax in your primary suite with his-hers entry to master bath and his-hers closets. The master bathroom is fully equipped with a separate tub and shower, double sinks, and plenty of under sink storage. Extra rooms add nice flex space for your everyday needs. The fenced in backyard gives you the perfect private area to enjoy the outdoors. This home also comes with unique characteristics: A sunroom with Lots of natural lighting and a dry bar that can be converted to a wet bar for entertaining guests. Don’t miss this incredible opportunity! Sellers are open to do a leaseback
